caption: Sometimes it's worth eating until you are overly full. This was one of those times!! The tacos were amazing. Especially the skirt steak there was so much flavor!  Everything was perfectly seasoned and tasted fresh.
Not worth $7 for size small horchata

Ordered from here 3 times in the last 10 days! So good. Everything we’ve tried has been so flavorful. I got the L&R salad with chicken tinga & can’t wait to get it again. We’ve tried the fish tacos, steak tacos, the guacamole, Frijoles Charros - everything has been delicious. Absolutely recommend giving this local biz a try!

Ordered on Uber eats. For starters false advertising, tacos don’t look nearly as good as they are pictured. Overpriced for regular run of the mill tacos. Order from any Mexican restaurant, you can get 3 tacos with rice and beans for $8-10 order. From here and you can get 3 tacos for $15 that aren’t any better than the tacos from next door. The sauce for the tacos is good don’t get me wrong but would have tasted better smothered in cheese. The corn in the elote was mushy and watery. Wasn’t aware until tonight that corn can be overcooked. Churros and horchata were good according to my sister!
Birria tacos are a MUST TRY !!!

We placed a large order at work today and the food came on time, hot, packaged well, and everything was correct. The birria tacos were a definite favorite, but honestly, all of these tacos were delicious. I will definitely order again and we had 30 very satisfied nurses at lunch time at work today.
order the birria tacos and thank me later
